<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Developer Tool Suite' }) %>
  <style>body { align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center; padding-top: 80px; }</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="dashboard-container">
    <%- include('partials/header', { pill: 'DASHBOARD', h1Left: 'Dev', h1Right: 'Toolkit', subtitle: 'Multi-purpose tools for developers. Fast, private, and local.' }) %>

    <div class="dashboard">
      <a href="/php-protector" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Security</span>
        <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
        <h2>PHP Protector</h2>
        <p>Obfuscate PHP projects recursively. Preserve directory structure and encrypt source code.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/image-resizer" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Images</span>
        <div class="icon">📐</div>
        <h2>Image Resizer</h2>
        <p>Professional image resizing with Cover, Contain, and Inside fitting. Recursive folder processing.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/image-converter" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Optimization</span>
        <div class="icon">🔄</div>
        <h2>Image Converter</h2>
        <p>Convert images to WebP, JPEG, PNG, or AVIF recursively. Dramatically reduce asset sizes.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/image-compressor" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Compression</span>
        <div class="icon">🗜️</div>
        <h2>Image Compressor</h2>
        <p>Shrink any image format — JPEG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, HEIC, TIFF, GIF, SVG. Quality presets + bulk folders.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/pdf-compressor" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Performance</span>
        <div class="icon">📄</div>
        <h2>PDF Compressor</h2>
        <p>Shrink large PDF folders with Ghostscript. Multiple quality levels with structure preservation.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/file-renamer" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Utility</span>
        <div class="icon">🏷️</div>
        <h2>Smart File Renamer</h2>
        <p>Clean and standardize filenames in bulk. Lowercase, replace spaces, strip special characters.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/code-minifier" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Code</span>
        <div class="icon">⚡</div>
        <h2>Code Minifier</h2>
        <p>Aggressively minify HTML, CSS, and Javascript. Mangle variables and strip whitespace.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="toast-container" id="toast-container"></div>
  <script src="/js/toast.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/shortcuts.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/cmd-palette.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/settings.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tour.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
